replies.body:
It really sounds like there are issues with your client not being able to create a stable link to the server during specific hours of the day. This often happens if there are ISP routing changes being made during peak hours in order to mitigate network congestion. Before we take a look at your route during the problematic period, we'll first want to ensure your local network settings are compatible with our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if you continue to see connection errors after completing that guide.
